## Phase 3: Admin/Teacher APIs
- [ ] `POST /api/admin/documents/requirements` — Create requirement
- [ ] `GET /api/admin/documents/requirements` — List requirements
- [ ] `PUT /api/admin/documents/requirements/[id]` — Edit requirement
- [ ] `DELETE /api/admin/documents/requirements/[id]` — Delete requirement
- [ ] `GET /api/admin/documents/submissions` — View all submissions
- [ ] `PUT /api/admin/documents/submissions/[id]/review` — Approve/Reject + comment
- [ ] `GET /api/admin/documents/submissions/[id]/download` — Secure download

## Phase 4: Student APIs
- [ ] `GET /api/student/documents` — List my required documents + status
- [ ] `POST /api/student/documents/upload` — Upload a document
- [ ] `PUT /api/student/documents/[id]/resubmit` — Re-upload after rejection

